### 8. Change password (requires authentication)
POST {{baseUrl}}/change-password/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "old_password": "password123",
  "new_password": "newpassword123",
  "confirm_password": "newpassword123"
}



### 9. Get user profile (requires authentication)
GET {{baseUrl}}/profile/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}


### 10. Update user profile (requires authentication)
PATCH  {{baseUrl}}/profile/update/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "first_name": "John Updated",
  "last_name": "Doe Updated",
  "bio": "I am a student learning new skills",
  "date_of_birth": "1995-05-15"
}

### 11. Delete user profile (requires authentication)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/profile/delete/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}


### 3. Logout using refresh token
# @name logout
POST {{baseUrl}}/logout/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "refresh": "{{refreshToken}}"
}



